lead_paragraph: England's shock defeat by Iceland in Nice and subsequent Euro 2016 exit on Monday suggested that the British government isn't the only national institution threatened with a leadership vacuum.

headline.print_headline: Leadership Crisis England's Big Concern After Iceland Loss
